explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the comparison between agile and traditional project management approaches, specifically examining decision criteria for adopting agile process models in firms within the DACH region. The study employs a quantitative approach, specifically a binary logistic regression model, to analyze data from 51 firms across nine industries. None of the provided keywords related to machine learning, deep learning, or other AI techniques are mentioned or implied in the title or abstract. The research is centered on project management methodologies and decision-making processes, not on any of the listed machine learning or AI topics.
